    <item>
      <title>丰业银行战略调整将重点关注北美</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/scotiabank-plans-to-focus-on-north-america-in-strategy-makeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新斯科舍银行计划将业务重心重新集中在北美，将资本从回报不佳的拉丁美洲业务转移出去，以争取更多客户的钱包。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/scotiabank-plans-to-focus-on-north-america-in-strategy-makeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 15:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金将获得美国证券交易委员会的新授权以集中清算美国国债交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/hedge-funds-to-get-new-sec-mandate-to-centrally-clear-us-treasuries-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会对对冲基金和经纪公司提出了新的要求，要求其在 26 万亿美元市场的结构性改革中集中清算更多的美国国债交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/hedge-funds-to-get-new-sec-mandate-to-centrally-clear-us-treasuries-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
